abstract: >
  SYNT_ISIC is a research-oriented software package for synthetic generation of dermatological
  images using diffusion models with integrated explainable AI (XAI) methods.
  It provides Time-SHAP, Integrated Gradients, SHAP, and Causal Shift Index (CSI)
  for attribution and causal validation of the generation process.
  The tool is intended solely for research purposes and is not a medical product.

